A: 1. Some products are not shown on the list because they enjoy the extended warranty without registration. Registration-free products include:
① Add-on cameras of NVRs. As long as you have registered the NVR, you will enjoy the 6-month extended warranty of its add-on cameras automatically; 
② Accessories. All accessories will enjoy a 2-year standard warranty and a 6-month extended coverage automatically; 
2. Products purchased over 2 years from the date of the invoice are not shown on the list; 
3. Devices that haven't been logged in are not shown on the list.

Currently, only phone number registered in China's mainland is supported. Please make sure; 
 Please open the mobile security software, temporarily disable the interception function, and then try to get verification code again; 
 You are recommended to exchange the SIM card to test. Insert your SIM card to someone else's phone to try to receive message again; 
 If the message gateway is congested or abnormal, the sent message will be delayed or lost. In that situation, we recommend you to contact the phone operator for verification, or try to get message again after a while.
